(482, 1, '2018-09-25 12:05:19', '2018-09-25 12:05:19', '<p>Logitech Control App provides exclusive information about the game, important information about the system status and remote management PC, so that you can play games not only on PC, but on a mobile device.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Features: </strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Exclusive information about the game on your mobile device in real time (for supported games)</li>\r\n	<li>Check the performance of your PC and important status information on your mobile device</li>\r\n	<li>Remote control of the media settings on your PC</li>\r\n	<li>View all installed games on your PC</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Logitech Control', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', 'logitech-control', '', '', '2018-11-02 18:53:24', '2018-11-02 15:53:24', '', 0, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/SoftWareSolutionsWP/?p=482', 0, 'post', '', 0),
