(644, 1, '2018-11-02 17:38:18', '2018-11-02 14:38:18', '<p>Logitech Control App provides exclusive information about the game, important information about the system status and remote management PC, so that you can play games not only on PC, but on a mobile device.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Features: </strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Exclusive information about the game on your mobile device in real time (for supported games)</li>\r\n	<li>Check the performance of your PC and important status information on your mobile device</li>\r\n	<li>Remote control of the media settings on your PC</li>\r\n	<li>View all installed games on your PC</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Logitech Control', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '482-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-02 17:38:18', '2018-11-02 14:38:18', '', 482, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/IT_blog/2018/11/02/482-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(645, 1, '2018-11-02 17:38:46', '2018-11-02 14:38:46', '<p>Best not an online game of the year in all of Europe!</p>\r\n<p>With the new design!</p>\r\n<p>Find out the most intimate secrets of his friends which they would never have been told. With this game fun guaranteed - because everyone wants to know the truth about his friends. The rules are simple, but will only be able to play the most persistent - to speak only the truth and nothing but the truth! </p>', 'Game of truth', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '484-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-02 17:38:46', '2018-11-02 14:38:46', '', 484, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/IT_blog/2018/11/02/484-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(646, 1, '2018-11-02 17:39:54', '2018-11-02 14:39:54', '<p>Project works since 2009.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Goals:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Development, implementation and support high load management system insurance company. System have to work with large number of users (more than 15000 users) and provide all business processes of insurance company. System have to provide configuration insurance products, reports without developers. System must to work using web-technologies and to provide 7-24 service.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Solution have all business processes for creation, support and management insurance contracts. </p>\r\n<p><strong>System include modules:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Insurance contract</li>\r\n	<li>Configuration of insurance products</li>\r\n	<li>Configuration of reports</li>\r\n	<li>CRM</li>\r\n	<li>E-insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Insurance service payment</li>\r\n	<li>Account with insurance broker and agent</li>\r\n	<li>Workplace agent/broker</li>\r\n	<li>Payment insurance services with bankcard</li>\r\n	<li>System administration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Expansion of project:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Development of mobile application</li>\r\n	<li>Integration with others client''s software and site</li>\r\n	<li>Integration with contact center (API phone)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong> ASP.NET Webforms, Web API, WCF, SOAP, ADO.Net, LINQ, Web Services, JSON, AJAX, DevExpress, JS, HTML</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mobile:</strong> Java for Android</p>\r\n<p><strong>Frameworks</strong> ASP.Net, Entity Framework</p>\r\n<p><strong>DB:</strong> MS SQL</p>\r\n<p>Now project is in support and development</p>', 'MANAGEMENT SYSTEM INSURANCE COMPANY', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '486-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-02 17:39:54', '2018-11-02 14:39:54', '', 486, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/IT_blog/2018/11/02/486-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(647, 1, '2018-11-02 17:41:20', '2018-11-02 14:41:20', '<p>Project works since 2016.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Customer: </strong>International Corporation</p>\r\n<p><strong>Goals: </strong></p>\r\n<p>Creating a logically unified information space for the management of supply and sale in real time. Getting plan and account information on the every level of company management. For achievement goals need to realize integration all solutions which using in company. Main software’s in company are Windchil, Vendavo, SAP, PRM, E-leader and LPOS. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Main system modules:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Product Management</li>\r\n	<li>Supply and Demand</li>\r\n	<li>Market Analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Sales Target</li>\r\n	<li>Order Status</li>\r\n	<li>Main KPI</li>\r\n	<li>Administration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong> ASP.net MVC, Web API, WCF, SOAP, ADO.Net, LINQ, Web Services, JSON, AJAX, DevExpress, JS, HTML</p>\r\n<p><strong>Frameworks:</strong> ASP.Net, Entity Framework</p>\r\n<p><strong>DB:</strong> MS SQL</p>', 'MANAGEMENT SYSTEM FOR SUPPLY AND SALE', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '496-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-02 17:41:20', '2018-11-02 14:41:20', '', 496, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/IT_blog/2018/11/02/496-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(648, 1, '2018-11-02 17:41:40', '2018-11-02 14:41:40', '<p>Project works since 2016.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Customer: </strong>bank</p>\r\n<p><strong>Goal:</strong><br />\r\nThe system allows custom authentication and authorization based upon an LDAP directory. In an organization, users and groups are stored in an LDAP directory. All the intranet applications are supposed to use this directory for authentication and authorization, to implement SSO. Development of common system for these applications to use for such authentication and authorization. A user if logged-in into one application, he should be able to use the other application w/o re-login.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>The system is composed of the following components: </p>\r\n<p>1. Web application</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Contains a log in page where users accessing intranet applications are redirected for authentication</li>\r\n	<li>Authenticates users against the LDAP directory, for the log in page</li>\r\n	<li>Keeps track of currently authenticated users, for later validations</li>\r\n	<li>Provides authorization data like user groups</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>2. HTTP module</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Provides custom authentication and authorization for the .NET applications</li>\r\n	<li>Authenticates every request to an application</li>\r\n	<li>Reporting</li>\r\n	<li>Administration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong> Webforms, Web API, WCF, WPF, SOAP, Web Services, JSON, AJAX, JS,HTML</p>\r\n<p><strong>Frameworks:</strong> ASP.Net, DevExpress XPO</p>\r\n<p><strong>DB:</strong> MS SQL</p>', 'CREATE THE ARCHITECTURE AND DESIGN OF AN LDAP BASED SINGLE SIGN ON SYSTEM (SSO). IMPLEMENT THE SYSTEM’S SERVICES AND APPLICATIONS', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '494-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-02 17:41:40', '2018-11-02 14:41:40', '', 494, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/IT_blog/2018/11/02/494-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(649, 1, '2018-11-02 17:44:19', '2018-11-02 14:44:19', '<p>Project works since 2015.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Customer: </strong>government institution</p>\r\n<p><strong>Goals:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Development of management system document for the hierarchical organization. Organization must be able to work without paper document. Company management have to get full control on the all stages work with document and task. System have to work with large number of users (more than 15000 users) and to save all documents of customs. System have to provide configuration workflow of document, reports without developers. System must to work using web-technologies and to provide 7-24 service. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>System to provide work with main functions of document workflow:</li>\r\n	<li>Registration of documents</li>\r\n	<li>Document workflow on the all stages document processing</li>\r\n	<li>Configuration of document workflow</li>\r\n	<li>Control of execution</li>\r\n	<li>Workflow for the citizen’s appeals</li>\r\n	<li>Creation of document project</li>\r\n	<li>Electronic archive of documents</li>\r\n	<li>Configuration workflow for the document</li>\r\n	<li>Configuration report</li>\r\n	<li>Integration with others company’s solutions</li>\r\n	<li>System administration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong> ASP.net MVC, Web API, WCF, SOAP, ADO.Net, LINQ, Web Services, JSON, AJAX, DevExpress, JS, HTML</p>\r\n<p><strong>Frameworks:</strong> ASP.Net, Entity Framework</p>\r\n<p><strong>DB:</strong> MS SQL / Oracle / PostgreSQL</p>', 'MANAGEMENT SYSTEM DOCUMENT', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '492-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-02 17:44:19', '2018-11-02 14:44:19', '', 492, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/IT_blog/2018/11/02/492-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(650, 1, '2018-11-02 17:44:35', '2018-11-02 14:44:35', '<p>Project works since 2014.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Customer: </strong>government institution</p>\r\n<p><strong>Goals: </strong></p>\r\n<p>Formations database of user actions on the base packages sent his computers to the network. System have to form database about all actions of user in network and to save this information long time. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Automatic processing of each packets sent user''s computer in the network</li>\r\n	<li>Automatic building the session of each user on the network</li>\r\n	<li>Automatic creation of report with date, time, data (IP address, port, MAC address) sender and recipient</li>\r\n	<li>Analysis session data on the defined rules, information about his violation</li>\r\n	<li>Definition hacker parameters who try to penetrate in to corporate network</li>\r\n	<li>Automatic functioning without administrator and the ability to define holes in information security</li>\r\n	<li>Processing data in others topology (local and cloud)</li>\r\n	<li>Reporting</li>\r\n	<li>System administration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>System architecture built by using technology Big Data.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Programming language: </strong>Java EE </p>\r\n<p><strong>Frameworks:</strong> Hadoop, Apache Storm</p>\r\n<p><strong>DB:</strong> Hbase (NoSQL)</p>', 'ANALYSIS OF NETWORK TRAFFIC', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '490-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-02 17:44:35', '2018-11-02 14:44:35', '', 490, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/IT_blog/2018/11/02/490-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(651, 1, '2018-11-02 17:44:49', '2018-11-02 14:44:49', '<p>Project works since 2012.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Customer: </strong>insurance broker</p>\r\n<p><strong>Goals:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Development, implementation e-insurance and management system for insurance broker. System have to provide the configuration for products e-insurance. Solution must to work with large number of users (more than 10000) and to provide 7-24 service. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Our solution include next functionality:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sell e-insurance to client</li>\r\n	<li>Payment services with bankcard</li>\r\n	<li>Personal account of customer with his history of e-insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Configuration e-insurance and set up on the site</li>\r\n	<li>Integration with others software solutions</li>\r\n	<li>Configuration of report</li>\r\n	<li>CRM</li>\r\n	<li>Reporting</li>\r\n	<li>Administration of system</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong> ASP.net MVC, Web API, WCF, SOAP, ADO.Net, LINQ, Web Services, JSON, AJAX, DevExpress, JS, HTML</p>\r\n<p><strong>Frameworks:</strong> ASP.Net, Entity Framework</p>\r\n<p><strong>DB:</strong> MS SQL</p>', 'E-INSURANCE AND MANAGEMENT SYSTEM INSURANCE BROKER', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '488-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-02 17:44:49', '2018-11-02 14:44:49', '', 488, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/IT_blog/2018/11/02/488-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(652, 1, '2018-11-02 17:59:11', '2018-11-02 14:59:11', '<p><strong>Segment:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Electronics, Embedded systems </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Electronic shooting gallery based on computer vision and laser gun. Complex system based on two parts: hardware and desktop application. The goal of project is to train soldiers, especially shooting skills. Advantages of such solution comparing with real shooting gallery: </p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>There is no necessity of specially equipped room</li>\r\n	<li>Much lower safety requirements</li>\r\n	<li>No consumables</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to use, even for fun</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Hardware part consists of laser gun (Arduino-based) and camera. Software part uses camera and provides analysis of detected shots. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Development segment:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Computer vision: camera support, frames acquisition, image filtering, recognition &amp; analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Adaptive algorithms &amp; logic</li>\r\n	<li>GUI</li>\r\n	<li>Arduino</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies:</strong>Delphi, C++, CUDA</p>', 'Electronic shooting gallery', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '468-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-02 17:59:11', '2018-11-02 14:59:11', '', 468, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/IT_blog/2018/11/02/468-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(653, 1, '2018-11-02 17:59:53', '2018-11-02 14:59:53', '<p><strong>Segment:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Electronics, Embedded systems </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Low-price pilotless aircraft built on ARM/STM32 microcontroller. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Responsibilities at project:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Board layout design</li>\r\n	<li>STM32 microcontroller programming</li>\r\n	<li>Designed communication between microcontroller and management board of motors</li>\r\n	<li>Developed board to communicate with the host device radio module</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies:</strong>IAR, C++, ARM/STM32</p>', 'Low-price pilotless aircraft', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '466-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-02 17:59:53', '2018-11-02 14:59:53', '', 466, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/IT_blog/2018/11/02/466-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(654, 1, '2018-11-02 18:00:25', '2018-11-02 15:00:25', '<p><strong>Segment:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Electronics, Embedded systems </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>The computer system allows you to monitor objects remotely using the wireless technology WiFi. With the help of the developed system user can be at a distance, but have visual contact with the object that should be observed using video viewing on any device. The developed system, can be improved by various sensors: gyroscope, accelerometer, magnetometer, etc.; be static (placed on a fixed platform), or to be placed on any platform from children''s toys - cars, quadrocopter and finally with a regular car or any military equipment. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Remote control &amp; video-monitoring</li>\r\n	<li>Moving platform</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to extend platform with any kind of sensors</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Details:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Board layout designed</li>\r\n	<li>STM32 microcontroller programming</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong>C++, ARM/STM32, OpenWRT</p>', 'WIFI ROBOT', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '464-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-02 18:00:25', '2018-11-02 15:00:25', '', 464, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/IT_blog/2018/11/02/464-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(655, 1, '2018-11-02 18:00:40', '2018-11-02 15:00:40', '<p><strong>Segment:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Electronics, Embedded systems </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Vending System creation for 8-channel control washing machines and dryers.</p>\r\n<p>STM32F207 processor, ZigBee CC2350 modules, GSM-modem SIM800C, bill acceptor ICT004, 4x20 display.</p>\r\n<p>We used the Kei-RTX RTOS </p>\r\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Remote control</li>\r\n	<li>Data analysis</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Details:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Board layout designed</li>\r\n	<li>STM32 microcontroller programming</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong>Microprocessor - STM32, C</p>', 'MANAGING CONTROLLER AUTOMATIC LAUNDRY', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '458-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-02 18:00:40', '2018-11-02 15:00:40', '', 458, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/IT_blog/2018/11/02/458-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(656, 1, '2018-11-02 18:01:33', '2018-11-02 15:01:33', '<p><strong>Segment:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Electronics, Embedded systems </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Creation of software for monitoring the supply and removal of body fluids during endoscopic interventions.<br />\r\nProcessors STM32F429, STM32F030, 800x480 display, 3-phase motor BLDS, strain gauges fluid pressure</p>\r\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Remote control</li>\r\n	<li>Data analysis</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Details:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Board layout designed</li>\r\n	<li>STM32 microcontroller programming</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries: </strong>Microprocessor - STM32F429, STM32F030, C</p>', 'ENDOSCOPIC IRRIGATION PUMP', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '456-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-02 18:01:33', '2018-11-02 15:01:33', '', 456, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/IT_blog/2018/11/02/456-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(657, 1, '2018-11-02 18:01:58', '2018-11-02 15:01:58', '<p><strong>Segment:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Electronics, Embedded systems </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Creating a household ultrasonic gas meter with a display of the results on the graphic display 320x240.</p>\r\n<p>The project was implemented on the basis of MSP430F2118 and time-to-digital converter ACAM GP21.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Remote control</li>\r\n	<li>Data analysis</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Details:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Board layout designed</li>\r\n	<li>Microcontroller programming</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong>MSP430F2118, ACAM GP21, C</p>', 'ULTRASONIC GAS FLOW METER', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '379-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-02 18:01:58', '2018-11-02 15:01:58', '', 379, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/IT_blog/2018/11/02/379-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(658, 1, '2018-11-02 18:02:17', '2018-11-02 15:02:17', '<p><strong>Segment:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Electronics, Embedded systems </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Collecting data (moisture, light, temperature) in real-time from sensors.</p>\r\n<p>Data is transmitted via broadband LoRa at a specified interval in real-time too.</p>\r\n<p>The system allows to set the data transmission interval from the server. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Remote control</li>\r\n	<li>Data analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to extend platform with any kind of sensors</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Details:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Board layout designed</li>\r\n	<li>Atmel SAMD11 microcontroller programming</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong>Microprocessor - Atmel SAMD11, LoRa, C</p>', 'SOIL SENSOR PROJECT', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '364-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-02 18:02:17', '2018-11-02 15:02:17', '', 364, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/IT_blog/2018/11/02/364-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(659, 1, '2018-11-02 18:02:29', '2018-11-02 15:02:29', '<p><strong>Segment:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Electronics, Embedded systems </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>The determinant of impurities in the product stream during cleaning.<br />\r\nCount and size analysis and the number of foreign particles in real time.</p>\r\n<p>The project was completed on the STM32F103 and display 128x64. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Remote control</li>\r\n	<li>Data analysis</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Details:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Board layout designed</li>\r\n	<li>STM32F103 microcontroller programming</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong>STM32F103, C</p>', 'OPTICAL ANALYZER DEGREE OF CLEANING LIQUIDS', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '318-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-02 18:02:29', '2018-11-02 15:02:29', '', 318, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/IT_blog/2018/11/02/318-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(660, 1, '2018-11-02 18:02:51', '2018-11-02 15:02:51', '<p><strong>Segment:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Electronics, Embedded systems </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Development of software for the control stand - multichannel acquisition and processing of information from the temperature sensors, pressure, mass flow meters, and control of the frequency converter for the pressure pump motor power.</p>\r\n<p>The processes are controlled using Free RTOS </p>\r\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Remote control</li>\r\n	<li>Data analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to extend platform with any kind of sensors</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Details:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Board layout designed</li>\r\n	<li>Microcontroller programming</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries: </strong>Microprocessor - Processors EFM32LC256, EFM32HG210 and ADC ADS1248, C</p>', 'STAND FOR THE CERTIFICATION OF THERMAL ENERGY METERS', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '314-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-02 18:02:51', '2018-11-02 15:02:51', '', 314, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/IT_blog/2018/11/02/314-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(661, 1, '2018-11-02 18:02:54', '2018-11-02 15:02:54', '<p><strong>Segment:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Electronics, Embedded systems </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Analysis of real-time transient and steady-harmonic components of current and voltage for a 3-phase network.<br />\r\nThe project was implemented on the basis of STM32F407 processor and AD7608 ADC using Keil-RTX RTOS.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>Details:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Board layout designed</li>\r\n	<li>STM32F407 microcontroller programming</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong>Microprocessor - STM32F407, C</p>', 'Fourier harmonics analyzer for high-power systems', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '316-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-02 18:02:54', '2018-11-02 15:02:54', '', 316, 'http://demo.pinofran.com/demo/IT_blog/2018/11/02/316-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
