(903, 1, '2018-11-05 14:57:44', '2018-11-05 11:57:44', '<p><strong>Segment:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Electronics, Embedded systems </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Collecting data (moisture, light, temperature) in real-time from sensors.</p>\r\n<p>Data is transmitted via broadband LoRa at a specified interval in real-time too.</p>\r\n<p>The system allows to set the data transmission interval from the server. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Remote control</li>\r\n	<li>Data analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to extend platform with any kind of sensors</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Details:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Board layout designed</li>\r\n	<li>Atmel SAMD11 microcontroller programming</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong>Microprocessor - Atmel SAMD11, LoRa, C</p>\r\nThe sensor enables you to sense soil moisture, temperature and the light spectrum wirelessly.The sensor is capable to work in both indoor and outdoor agricultural environments.\r\nExample Applications\r\n– Agricultural crop monitoring, i.e. tomatoes, asparagus, flower bulbs\r\n– Lawn water management', 'System for the agriculture', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '870-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-05 14:57:44', '2018-11-05 11:57:44', '', 870, 'http://blog.softsln.net/web-and-print-design/870-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(905, 1, '2018-11-05 15:00:17', '2018-11-05 12:00:17', '<p><strong>Segment:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Electronics, Embedded systems </p>\r\n<p><strong>Short description:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Collecting data in real-time from sensors.</p>\r\n<p>Data is transmitted via broadband LoRa at a specified interval in real-time too.\r\nThe sensor enables you to sense soil moisture, temperature and the light spectrum wirelessly.</p>\r\n<p>The system allows to set the data transmission interval from the server. \r\nThe sensor is capable to work in both indoor and outdoor agricultural environments. </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Remote control</li>\r\n	<li>Data analysis</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to extend platform with any kind of sensors</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Details:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Board layout designed</li>\r\n	<li>Atmel SAMD11 microcontroller programming</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nExample Applications\r\n– Agricultural crop monitoring, i.e. tomatoes, asparagus, flower bulbs\r\n– Lawn water management\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Technologies and libraries:</strong>Microprocessor - Atmel SAMD11, LoRa, C</p>\r\n', 'System for the agriculture', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '870-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-05 15:00:17', '2018-11-05 12:00:17', '', 870, 'http://blog.softsln.net/web-and-print-design/870-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
